Product info : Aviagen provides day-old grandparent and parent stock chicks to customers in 130 countries worldwide under the Arbor Acres, Indian River, and Ross brand names.. Aviagen specializes in poultry genetics.. Aviagen offers a full portfolio of breeding stock under the Arbor Acres®, Indian River® and Ross® brand names. The Rowan Range® and Specialty Males® target slower-growing and other niche market needs. 
Useful info : Aviagen is committed to breeding success, health and biosecurity, global security of supply, compartmentalization, welfare, and sustainability. They also offer customer support, production management schools, and research and development.
